{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1608/comments/7262191.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:ede6017e2138..c29dc3c66cd8?path=gazebo%2Fcommon%2FSVGLoader_TEST.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1608/_/diff#comment-7262191"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1608, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1608.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1608"}}, "title": "SVG support for arcs, disjoints paths and their triangulation / extrusion"}, "content": {"raw": "For portability, it's nice to use `boost::filesystem` with the `/` operator instead of using \"/\" characters. See [examples_build.cc](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/5b7f3c2a02db5310b167675b018cce53341ca806/test/examples/examples_build.cc?at=default#cl-40) for an example.\n\n~~~\n  boost::filesystem::path filePath = std::string(PROJECT_SOURCE_PATH);\n  path /= std::string(\"test\");\n  path /= std::string(\"data\");\n  path /= std::string(\"svg\");\n  path /= std::string(\"arc_circle.svg\");\n~~~", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>For portability, it's nice to use <code>boost::filesystem</code> with the <code>/</code> operator instead of using \"/\" characters. See <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/5b7f3c2a02db5310b167675b018cce53341ca806/test/examples/examples_build.cc?at=default#cl-40\" rel=\"nofollow\">examples_build.cc</a> for an example.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">boost</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">filesystem</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">path</span> <span class=\"nt\">filePath</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">PROJECT_SOURCE_PATH</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">/=</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;test&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">/=</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;data&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">/=</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;svg&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">path</span> <span class=\"o\">/=</span> <span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;arc_circle.svg&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-03T01:02:29.283723+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": 174, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/common/SVGLoader_TEST.cc"}, "updated_on": "2015-06-03T01:02:29.290903+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 7262191}